cat << EOF
XFce 4 is a lightweight dektop environment based on GTK2. This is a library
required by all other xfce4 modules. It provides several useful non-gui
functions and some header files that make the build process of xfce 4 modules
a bit more consistent (i18n, debugging, ...).
